your corsage.

39:19.733 --> 39:22.694
I must have left it
in my dorm fridge.

39:23.695 --> 39:25.697
[Belly] It's okay.

39:25.781 --> 39:26.948
[Taylor] We got to go.

39:27.032 --> 39:28.283
[Steven] Yes. Yes.

39:28.366 --> 39:29.910
[Laurel] Beck, it's time
for them to head out.

39:29.993 --> 39:31.912
I'm just going to get
a couple last pictures, okay?

39:31.995 --> 39:33.997
I'm heading up to you tomorrow,
first thing.

39:34.081 --> 39:36.291
- [Susannah] Have fun, everyone.
- [call beeps off]

39:36.374 --> 39:39.586
