everyone wants me to be?

41:12.846 --> 41:14.598
No.

41:14.681 --> 41:16.725
Not me.

41:18.810 --> 41:21.104
[sighs] This is all my fault.

41:23.940 --> 41:26.276
I got so excited

41:26.359 --> 41:29.029
