41:40.624 --> 41:43.668
You and Conrad will never let
anything come between you.

41:44.920 --> 41:47.464
You will always
put each other first.

41:48.632 --> 41:51.051
Mom, Con and I are fine.
I promise.

41:51.134 --> 41:54.262
You don't have to worry
about that, okay? She chose him.

41:54.346 --> 41:56.514
They-they chose each other
and I'm...

41:57.891 --> 41:59.726
I'm, I'm...

41:59.809 --> 42:01.937
Her best friend.

42:02.020 --> 42:05.148
This is just the beginning
of your story, Jere.

42:06.149 --> 42:09.319
