of the story goes.

42:22.249 --> 42:25.001
Do you know what
my graduation quote was?

42:25.085 --> 42:27.420
Amelia Earhart.

42:29.089 --> 42:32.008
"Adventure is
worthwhile in itself."

42:33.885 --> 42:35.387
Remember that.

42:36.513 --> 42:38.682
I adore you, sunshine boy.

42:39.975 --> 42:41.393
