who ever really saw me.

42:47.691 --> 42:49.901
Her and Belly.

42:49.985 --> 42:52.737
So, um...

42:52.821 --> 42:54.364
What are you saying?

42:56.533 --> 42:58.868
I don't know, Bells,
it's complicated.

43:00.704 --> 43:02.372
That thing you said earlier?

43:03.415 --> 43:05.625
About "adventure is worthwhile"?

43:08.169 --> 43:10.297
Did my mom tell you about that?

43:11.548 --> 43:13.049
No, I...

43:13.133 --> 43:15.135
